GRANT BY WILLIAM DE BONVILLE TO MARGAN ABBEY OF LAND HELD BY THE TEMPLARS IN THE TIME OF HIS FATHER.

[MARGAM CHARTER]

Omnibus Sancte e. f. a. q. p. s. pervenerit . WILLELMUS de BONEVILLA . filius J OHANNIS de BONAVILLA . salutem.

Sciatis me concessisse et hac carta . confirmasse Deo et ecclesie Sancte MARm de MARGAN et m. i. D. s. in p. et perpetuam elemosinam .
